prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: I wanted to start a podcast.  I have a lot of knowledge about fantasy football.  I wanted to share my knowledge with the world.  I decided to research by looking at how other fantasy football podcasters do their shows.  Looking up different kinds of software was the next step.  Adobe suite was my preference.
